      {
        "id": "row-opening",
        "cells": [1],
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "col-opening",
            "contents": [
              {
                "id": "text-hi",
                "type": "heading",
                "values": {
                  "containerPadding": "40px 40px 25px",
                  "headingType": "h1",
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "fontSize": "28px",
                  "color": "#2C3E50",
                  "fontFamily": {
                    "label": "Cormorant Garamond",
                    "value": "'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif",
                    "url": "https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600&display=swap"
                  },
                  "textAlign": "left",
                  "lineHeight": "160%",
                  "text": "{{contact.first_name}},",
                  "hideDesktop": false
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "text-intro-1",
                "type": "text",
                "values": {
                  "containerPadding": "0px 40px 15px",
                  "text": "<p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A4A4A;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;margin:0;\">I wanted to share something with you that I think might help as you continue exploring venues.</p>",
                  "hideDesktop": false
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "text-intro-2",
                "type": "text",
                "values": {
                  "containerPadding": "0px 40px 15px",
                  "text": "<p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A4A4A;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;margin:0;\">When couples tour Cameron Estate — people just like you — they often tell me something interesting: they knew within the first few minutes whether it was right for them. Not because we have the fanciest ballroom in Lancaster County, or the most acres, or the highest search ranking.</p>",
                  "hideDesktop": false
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "text-intro-3",
                "type": "text",
                "values": {
                  "containerPadding": "0px 40px 0px",
                  "text": "<p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:#4A4A4A;font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;margin:0;\">They knew because they could genuinely picture their wedding happening here. They weren't looking at <em>a</em> wedding anymore — they were seeing <em>their</em> wedding.</p>",
                  "hideDesktop": false
                }
              }
            ],
            "values": {}
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#FDFCFA",
          "columnsBackgroundColor": "",
          "padding": "0px"
        }
